    protected abstract static class BaseRedSynchronizer.FutureTransformer<RETURN_CLASSIFIER extends BaseRedSynchronizer.ReturnClassifier>
extends Object
    A middleware class to manipulate and transform future status. This middleware will enable the caller to set the type of the expected result of futures by calling either one of the transformation methods: succeed(), finish() or fail, which expect all preconditions to respectively succeed, finish either by success or failure, or to fail. Preconditions are receive as either BaseRedSynchronizer.Result or BaseRedSynchronizer.Marker, and when and transformation method is called, a BaseRedSynchronizer.ReturnClassifier middleware instance is returned.
